        <div class="industries__header">
          <h5>Full-featured APIs</h5>
          <h2>Make them look good on all screens.</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          Wherever you sell and market your products, Solidus will support you. Use the built-in RESTful and GraphQL APIs to create an amazing customer experience across all customer touchpoints. Synchronize your product catalog and user interactions with the major social and marketing platforms for a holistic presence in your customers’ life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-block pb-0">
  <div class="industries testimonials">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="carousel-content">
        <div class="main-image-container">
